{"tid":1772506,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平冬天帶頭下渠挖冰打土壩","createTime":"2019-12-06T16:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T07:56:08.000Z","uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd7ad4b43a3fde1d71d62bdc60809b618005419","tid":1772506,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"當選村支書 冬天帶頭下渠挖冰打土壩<br />\n<br />\n1969年1月，習近平插隊落戶到陝西省延川縣一個名叫梁家河的小山村。1974年1月入黨後不久，習近平即被選為梁家河村大隊黨支部書記。他帶領社員到寨子渠打壩，當時天寒地凍，打壩的河渠裡冰塊很厚，不處理掉，壩基不穩，春天一融化，壩就容易坍塌，會造成勞民傷財。在工地上，習近平做了下渠挖冰塊的動員。但由於天氣寒冷刺骨，社員們沒有行動。習近平二話不說，第一個跳進冰水裡往外搬冰塊。幹了一陣兒，群眾感動了，紛紛脫掉棉襖、棉褲下了河。習近平帶領社員們日夜奮戰，給村裡打了十幾個土壩，治理了多條爛溝。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddacb19c7685b677068d0de0282803ef1710fdd","tid":1772506,"uid":63670,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"一開頭起好個壩咪得lo"},{"pid":"7219f3c1c678a5e62e041687e6e7dfe018a7fedb","tid":1772506,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢全部呢幾年改過"},{"pid":"7eb9c0d9e909518ea95d74e3af6ebd5c244a788c","tid":1772506,"uid":240518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fddacb19c7685b677068d0de0282803ef1710fdd","tid":1772506,"uid":63670,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"一開頭起好個壩咪得lo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53b1b0b74a7e9f10109e74bde13227fe2b598db","tid":1772506,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T23:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1Bg9NU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1Bg9NU.gif&h=5666855a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bktn4YN.gif\" />